dct_description_sm: Shows land use. 'Prepared by TVA, Division of Forestry, Fisheries and Wildlife Development, Natural Resources Analysis Demonstrations; in cooperation with USDA Soil Conservation Service and TVA, Division of Agricultural Development; 1978.' 'Source: USDA Soil Conservation Service, Fayette County, Tennessee Soil Survey; 1964. 'Grid cell size: 3.75 seconds (approximately 2.68 acres). Originally printed 8 cells/inch vertically and 10 cells/inch horizontally, approximating the geodetic proportions of a polyconic projection in the latitude depicted.' Includes key map.
